{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230200/extras/add_to_wishlist.gif?t=1740306862\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230200/extras/horizontal_line.png?t=1740306862\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Forgotten Heroes is a roguelike turn-based RPG where you can create infinitely deep custom characters, build a team of 4 heroes, slay monsters, collect loot, and shape your own story. Choose your adventure path and dive into a world of strategy, exploration, and epic battles!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230200/extras/gif_1.gif?t=1740306862\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">About Forgotten Heroes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Forgotten Heroes is an immersive adventure that allows players to customize their characters with unique appearances, stats, talents, and abilities. You can craft heroes with endless depth, giving each character their own unique playstyle and strengths.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230200/extras/gif_2.gif?t=1740306862\" /> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Embark on an endless adventure, exploring procedurally generated levels, battling monsters, and gathering loot to grow stronger. Visit shops like the armory and potion lab to upgrade gear, choose random items to boost heroes after each level, and start each run with a unique blessing. Build a team of four heroes from characters like magicians and warriors, strategizing with their stats and abilities to overcome a variety of enemies.</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamst