 their characters with unique appearances, stats, talents, and abilities. You can craft heroes with endless depth, giving each character their own unique playstyle and strengths.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230200/extras/gif_2.gif?t=1740306862\" /> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Embark on an endless adventure, exploring procedurally generated levels, battling monsters, and gathering loot to grow stronger. Visit shops like the armory and potion lab to upgrade gear, choose random items to boost heroes after each level, and start each run with a unique blessing. Build a team of four heroes from characters like magicians and warriors, strategizing with their stats and abilities to overcome a variety of enemies.</p>","developers":["Hard Shark Games"],"genres":[{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"RPG","id":"3"},{"description":"Strategy","id":"2"},{"description":"Early Access","id":"70"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230200/header.jpg?t=1740306862","is_free":false,"legal_notice":"\u00a9 2025 Hard Shark Games. All rights reserved.","linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"mac_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257054862,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257054862/movie480.mp4?t=1726824167","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257054862/movie_max.mp4?t=1726824167"},"name":"Official Trailer","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257054862/movie.293x165.jpg?t=1726824167","webm":{"